Linked List Big O:

Prepend: Adding element to head = O(1)
Append: Adding element to tail = O(1)
Remove First: Removing element from head = O(1)
Remove last: Removing element from tail = O(1)

Insert: Adding element to specific index = O(n)
Remove: Removing element from specific index = O(n)

Lookup by Index: Fetch the value by index = O(n)
Lookup by Value: Fetch the actual value = O(n)

Basically acts as nested HashMap
